scene.message:
Yukino: Where's this?{nl}
It looks different from{nl}
the rooms before.{waitkey}{ret}

???: What have you come for,{nl}
humans...? Did you come{nl}
knowing this is the gate{waitkey}to the underworld,{waitkey}{clearbox}and that I am the watchdog{nl}
Cerberus?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What is this beast?{nl}
Does it mean to bar our way?{nl}
If so, I'll show no mercy!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: What's with this guy?{nl}
Trying to block my path?{nl}
What a stuck-up jerk.{waitkey}{clearbox}But he looks tough...{nl}
Let's try "talking" first!{nl}
Uh...{waitkey}{clearbox}"Me sama grumpy.{nl}
You there, move it."{nl}
...or something.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey, hey,{nl}
us Ayase and friends{nl}
don't really wanna{waitkey}fight you or anything.{waitkey}{clearbox}We just kinda wanna{nl}
get to the other side,{nl}
is all... No good?{waitkey}{ret}

Cerberus: Hmph.{nl}
Beyond here lies the world{nl}
of death - where the souls{waitkey}of the dead gather.{waitkey}{clearbox}I doubt the likes of you{nl}
have business there?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: The "world of the{nl}
dead," is it? How amusing.{nl}
This tower itself is already{waitkey}a "hell" where demons gather.{waitkey}{clearbox}There is nothing left{nl}
for us to fear now.{waitkey}{clearbox}Besides, the secret of our{nl}
lost Persona power from the{nl}
candle room may lie here.{waitkey}{clearbox}What Yuriko said back then -{nl}
"I've taken the life of{nl}
your other self"...{waitkey}{clearbox}referred to the loss of our{nl}
Persona power.{waitkey}{clearbox}"Taking the life" is "death."{nl}
"The death of one's other{nl}
self," and this place,{waitkey}"where dead souls gather"!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hmph. It's plain our "other{nl}
selves' souls" are here!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey, mutt! You're stalling us{nl}
on Yuriko's orders, aren't{nl}
you? Let us through!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Heehee. The secret of{nl}
the Persona lost in the candle{nl}
room seems to lie here.{waitkey}{clearbox}What Yuriko said then -{nl}
"I've taken the life of{nl}
your other self"...{waitkey}{clearbox}referred to the loss of{nl}
our Personas.{waitkey}{clearbox}"Taking the life" is "death."{nl}
"The death of one's other{nl}
self," and this place is{waitkey}"where dead souls gather"...{waitkey}{clearbox}Our "other selves' souls"{nl}
seem to be here.{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey! Cerberus!! You're{nl}
stalling us here on Yuriko's{nl}
orders, aren't you?{waitkey}{clearbox}Be quiet and let us through!{nl}
Or else...{waitkey}{ret}

Cerberus: You've got{nl}
good intuition.{waitkey}{clearbox}That reasoning is half right{nl}
and half wrong.{waitkey}{clearbox}Certainly, the Personas you{nl}
speak of are here.{waitkey}{clearbox}But I have nothing to do{nl}
with Yuriko. I simply guard{nl}
this place because I wish to.{waitkey}{clearbox}In the world of the dead I{nl}
watch over, half-baked souls{nl}
of the dead are not wanted.{waitkey}{clearbox}Take them as you please.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Understood.{nl}
We'll go through.{waitkey}{clearbox}We won't lay a hand{nl}
on you either.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: The world of the dead,{nl}
huh. Never thought I'd visit{nl}
while still alive.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Not a place I'd care{nl}
to visit of my own accord,{nl}
if I had no business there.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Whoa! The afterlife!{nl}
When we get back, let's go{nl}
on TV!{waitkey}{clearbox}"Uesugi saw it!! This is the{nl}
afterlife!" ...or something!{nl}
Dehyahyahyahya!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Hell, is it?{nl}
To see it while still alive{nl}
is rather Lucky!{waitkey}{ret}

Cerberus: The demons of{nl}
Tartarus are stronger than{nl}
those of the tower.{waitkey}{clearbox}They hate the living,{nl}
so be careful.{waitkey}{ret}
